WEBVTT

00:00.061 --> 00:01.211
Previously on Suits...

00:01.263 --> 00:03.455
Walter, I can't guarantee you
we'll win,

00:03.455 --> 00:06.841
but I can guarantee you
that I will never sell you out.

00:06.908 --> 00:08.828
Well, you told me that
Mike Ross wasn't a threat,

00:08.844 --> 00:10.364
and then he handcuffed us
with a T.R.O.

00:10.378 --> 00:12.463
I want proof that
he's giving up his bid,

00:12.547 --> 00:13.881
and if I don't get it
by the morning,

00:13.932 --> 00:15.549
I'm gonna call
my private investigators,

00:15.600 --> 00:16.550
and I'm gonna finish
what I started.

00:16.601 --> 00:18.185
What did Harvey tell you?

00:18.253 --> 00:19.653
Looks like
he told me the truth.

00:19.721 --> 00:21.021
We're done.

00:21.089 --> 00:23.274
I want you to stop
the personal attacks on Mike.

00:23.358 --> 00:25.038
You told me this
wasn't gonna be a problem.

00:25.060 --> 00:28.479
You don't have to stop this
because you're some changed man.

00:28.563 --> 00:30.564
You have to stop this
because you owe me.

00:30.632 --> 00:31.632
Mr. Ross.

00:31.633 --> 00:32.566
Eric Woodall.

00:32.616 --> 00:34.034
I'm the U.S. attorney for--

00:34.102 --> 00:35.453
The southern district
of New York.

00:35.537 --> 00:36.620
I know who you are.

00:36.705 --> 00:38.289
Since when does the S.E.C.
go around

00:38.373 --> 00:40.875
intimidating law firms
by going after their clients?

00:40.942 --> 00:42.076
They don't,
but they will

00:42.127 --> 00:43.728
when Eric Woodall starts there
next week.

00:43.745 --> 00:44.745
It started.

00:44.746 --> 00:47.548
Seven clients, seven subpoenas,

00:47.615 --> 00:49.133
all coming tomorrow.

00:51.000 --> 00:57.074
